## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
1. Open the app while online → confirm premium status is correctly synced.
2. Go to DevTools → Application → Local Storage → confirm all values are encrypted (unreadable base64 ciphertext instead of plain JSON).
3. Manually edit any encrypted value → refresh → confirm the app treats it as tampered (graceful fallback to defaults/logout).
4. Change the device clock backwards → refresh → confirm premium is revoked (monotonic time check).

### Manual Verification
- Test the full flow: Login → verify tokens encrypted → go offline → confirm premium still works → change clock back → confirm premium revoked.
